name: Smooth psychedelic seeds
description: The view of seeds from an abstract perspective, involving geometric and non-geometric forms, combined harmonically, showing intense colours that can be produced by plants. The sun in the centre as an essential element for the growing of life. A series of colours are shown melting, making reference to the changes that occur in seeds and its beauty. The result of this process is shown with the growing stems and green leaves that start with a rigid shape, then twisted to turn into flowers and other forms that are beautiful as well.
